Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All the pirates who are after the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...head for the New World, the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.19,0:02:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:03:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy and his crew reached Fishman Island located 10,000 meters below sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.95,0:03:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,where the New Fishman Pirates who are looking to destroy the Ryugu Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...assisted by Vander Decken, who is after Shirahoshi, are engaging in secret maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.19,0:03:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The Straw Hats find themselves caught up in the turmoil
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.82,0:03:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and Zoro, Usopp and Brook got caught by Hody at the Ryugu Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.16,0:03:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go to the Ryugu Palace to save my crew and kick that Hody guy's ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.47,0:03:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I said "Don't do it"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.14,0:03:48.15,B1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Something Has Happened to Hody! The True Power of the Evil Drug!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for the decisive battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, as soon as we cut the King's head off, the morale of his army will be shattered
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:03:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and then it's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.99,0:04:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means we'll have a new king soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, at Candy Factory Town in the center of the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:21.91,OS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,1000)}CANDY FACTORY
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Daruma-san, w-what are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.09,0:04:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,--He's chewing the wall of the factory... --W-What powerful jaws!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My fangs itch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.41,0:05:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want some trendy cappuccino and cake for my happy snack time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.95,0:05:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I look like a yuppie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry, Daruma-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.26,0:05:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to bite your flesh off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My favorite snack is the bones of big fish! And don't ever forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, I'll be careful from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.07,0:05:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay. I'm gonna go chew up the royal family and their soldiers now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.14,0:05:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,See you at Conchcorde Plaza!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We all have to be there! Don't be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.38,0:05:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do about the citizens?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you listening to what Boss said?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He said "No more stepping on her picture."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave them alone! They know what's waiting for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.61,0:06:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The New Fishman Pirates have...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...4 shark Fishman officers including Hody,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and 1 giant squid Fishman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, they have a blue-ringed octopus Merman as a bodyguard,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,who is the best swordsman on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Our only hope is the Neptune brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in the Princes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.87,0:06:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotsun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.14,0:06:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,At Waterwheel Town in the north of the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.14,0:06:30.84,OS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,1000)}WATERWHEEL TOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.81,0:06:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,--The Princes are heading to Conchcorde Plaza! --What's gonna happen to this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. All we wanted was friendly relations with humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should our lives be threatened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe they're gonna execute the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we stop them by taking these guys as hostages?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hostages?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.13,0:07:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not gonna work. Boss Hody is a ruthless man-kotsun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.74,0:07:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you try it, he'll just cut us off and go on as planned-kotsun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not good. Because he got beaten by the Princes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.08,0:07:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Dosun-san's power level went down to "kotsun."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He needs the Energy Steroid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always been like that-kotsun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He has too much pride-potsun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"Potsun"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.67,0:07:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't like Fishmen who do business with human pirates-posun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"Posun"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Those Fishmen who transfused blood to wounded humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,he punished them by attacking them in the dark-tosun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tosun"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.23,0:07:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans' blood is tainted-tosun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:08:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Both giving them blood and getting their blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.57,0:08:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...degrades our Fishman blood-dosun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.70,0:08:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's back to "dosun"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Those Fishmen who support the horrible humans are...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...getting in the way of...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.08,0:08:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...Our noble intentions-dokan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.49,0:08:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He exceeded "dosun"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.62,0:08:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He broke the chain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The soldiers got blown away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn Fukaboshi! I'll get even with you-bokan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll beat you to within an inch of your life next time-zugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, guys-bagon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,To Conchcorde Plaza, the execution ground-gaban!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.26,0:09:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,In front of the Fishman Cultural Hall in the south of the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.26,0:09:11.97,OS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,1000)}FISHMAN CULTURAL HALL
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.31,0:09:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did you say is drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You are, Hyouzou-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Get yourself back together! You can't fight like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No worries, no worries! This is my treat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.05,0:09:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to fight Neptune's army which is being led by Fukaboshi now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In the worst-case scenario, the infamous Jinbe will be there too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stand on your feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good. He's as slippery as a sea cucumber.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe how many degrees your head can spin around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.78,0:09:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not spinning! You're too drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.58,0:09:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy! I bet you can't even hold your sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:10:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.02,0:10:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stay away from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyouzou will slice into anyone when he gets drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He will... slice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He sliced his friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.67,0:10:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna cut more!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hyouzou-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:11:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to the plaza now and slice up the Neptunes to your heart's content!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.85,0:11:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oiaiyonohoniaiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.95,0:11:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.32,0:11:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,At the Marine Shopping Mall in the east of the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.32,0:11:14.99,OS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,1000)}MARINE SHOPPING MALL
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We're former soldiers of Neptune's army! We won't let you do whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! He disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.27,0:11:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.68,0:11:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He disappeared again! How can he do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.82,0:11:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you civilians do now? Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Zeo-san can change his skin color like a chameleon and camouflage himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.43,0:11:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's even hard for us to figure out where he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's impossible for us to beat a guy like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Your only hope is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Neptune brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But they'll die soon just like the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means you folk have...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a bug!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.96,0:12:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened? He stopped talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.44,0:12:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the cockroach dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.41,0:12:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's flattened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Which means you folk have nowhere to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nowhere to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.26,0:13:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He kept his nobility! He's not known as the Noble of the Fishman District for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he pretending as if nothing happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.54,0:13:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Later today, at Conchcorde Plaza,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the Neptune family will die and the new king will rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's go to the plaza!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Hody! Wh-What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.73,0:13:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,--It's nothing. --But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.60,0:13:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, bring it to me now! As much as we have!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You better not take more Energy Steroid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want your head to get smashed?! Just shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.09,0:13:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain! We got King Neptune already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Victory is within our grasp! So you don't have to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.29,0:14:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right! Don't push yourself too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm running out of time! I said "Get out of my way"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't! I said "Leave it up to me"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you understand even after I've explained it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.44,0:14:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't give a damn about the history between Fishmen and humans
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,when my friends are in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.84,0:14:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why! That is why I want you to wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They both wanna help the country and their friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.79,0:15:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do they have to fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.70,0:15:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How long will it take to Conchcorde Plaza?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.70,0:15:18.87,OS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,1000)}"WATERWHEEL TOWN" TO "CONCHCORDE PLAZA"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.67,0:15:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Less than an hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.97,0:15:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the actions of a sane man to go through the trouble of
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,executing the King at the plaza!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they just wanna lure you Princes out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.31,0:15:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I am looking forward to it, rather. I won't let them hurt my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.32,0:15:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And I won't let our people's minds close again, not after they were just opening up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I know why Jinbe always had his eyes on Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.76,0:15:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And they are the reason we haven't seen human pirates around the island these days!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Shirahoshi is still in the Hard Shell Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help worrying because we don't hear anything about her-fa-so-la-ti-do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:16:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Fukaboshi-sama, what do you think about the Straw Hats?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame Sharley said they will destroy this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They did not seem like they had bad intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat is Jinbe's friend and the Mermaids at the cove didn't speak badly of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.96,0:16:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Those Mermaids sure have an eye for people!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is not the time to think about those things!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right-la-ti-do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Summon all soldiers from all over the country! We will save the King at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.15,0:16:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,At Fishverly Hills in the northeast of the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:41.68,OS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,1000)}FISHVERLY HILLS
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.39,0:16:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that we are still struggling against just one sea monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There is something not right with this sea monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:17:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You damn fools, it serves you right! Good job, Sea Bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The Energy Steroid worked too well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Calm down, Sea Bear! That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.41,0:17:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Those soldiers are barely alive. So it's over, Sea Bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Use this! Sea monsters don't like fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Much?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.21,0:17:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikaros-san's body is contorting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.98,0:17:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it some kind of curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Put out the fire-ch, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.11,0:17:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, crackle, crackle...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire? What about the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become a piece of dried squid-ch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.56,0:17:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:18:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you were trying to roast me and eat me with sake. I'll kill you-ch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.80,0:18:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would do that, fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.57,0:18:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikaros-san once had a best friend who was a giant squid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, he went too close to the sun and became a giant dried squid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.31,0:18:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why when Ikaros-san sees fire, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Daidalos!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a Fishman. He's not gonna be like his friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Daida...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.73,0:18:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful hereafter-ch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That Dried Squid Spear is always waiting for its chance to turn back into a normal squid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.54,0:18:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So once it gets stuck in someone, it'll suck all fluid out of his body!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ika!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.05,0:18:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ika, Ika, Ika, Ika, Ika, Ika, Ika...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.72,0:19:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's awful! He's pummeling that guy who got dried out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.19,0:19:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikaros-san, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't we have to go to the plaza already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Much! You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late. He already became a dried squid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.47,0:19:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Minister of the Right! Look up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.61,0:19:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Hody and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see Hody but I see some men from the Fishman District!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.65,0:19:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They're heading to the plaza!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, those bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.95,0:19:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! The King-sama is on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.72,0:19:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,King Neptune-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Knight, perform a miracle to save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.16,0:19:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me Great Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.96,0:19:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't save my citizens--look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.93,0:19:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.17,0:19:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,King-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.44,0:19:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We are the King's army but we can't even protect the King?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, what are we here for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.01,0:19:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikaros-san! There are only 2 hours left until the execution!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with us to Conchcorde Plaza!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.82,0:20:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Captain Hody-ch?! I know he's there-ch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.92,0:20:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why doesn't he even come out-ch?! Much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.96,0:20:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.57,0:20:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That drug enhances your strength but takes years off your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't take it in the first place-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.41,0:20:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Hody said he got cut by the pirate swordsman and it hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut? The Boss got cut?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.18,0:20:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So he kept taking the Energy Steroid to kill the pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.89,0:20:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And he ended up... I mean, we told him to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.33,0:20:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.54,0:20:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't... breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.64,0:20:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My body is gonna explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.27,0:21:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Much! Is it a side-effect-ch?! So that drug could kill you as I thought-ch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.42,0:21:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.16,0:21:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong, Sea Bear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.50,0:21:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He's acting strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.14,0:22:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Although all these sea monsters are under Captain Hody's control,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.67,0:22:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen them get so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.18,0:22:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,--C-Captain Hody?! --Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.22,0:22:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why shouldn't I be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.36,0:22:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.81,0:22:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see some soldiers from the army!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.11,0:22:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Water Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.05,0:23:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Facing the destructive power of Hody's new form,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.62,0:23:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Neptune's army is defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.52,0:23:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The citizens have only one hope remaining...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.56,0:23:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The three Neptune brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.30,0:23:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They rise to face Hody, and their battle begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.33,0:23:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.60,0:23:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Battle is on! At Conchcorde Plaza!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.51,0:23:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
